 個故仔<br />\nbtw對我黎講冇左個尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n玩過3部曲only"},{"pid":"84f2b167473b3e027fbe79528ff36f6c9f1fe22e","tid":896672,"uid":217092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T09:12:21.000Z","msg":"其實刺客啲game好多時都係一集新系統-&gt;下一集完善翻個系統 之後loop<br />\n例子係ac2-&gt;brotherhood,revelations<br />\nac3-&gt;ac4, rogue <br />\nunity-&gt;syndicate<br />\norigin-&gt;odyssey <br />\n個人覺得通常佢試新系統果集都伏伏地(除咗ac2)<br />\n原因係佢擺曬啲資源執個新系統  搞到啲side quest太重覆 個劇情又會悶到仆街"},{"pid":"5f8ed06077860381ffc0aee59c4fc3d8839df2b5","tid":896672,"uid":54656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T17:28:55.000Z","msg":"最新個集大家點睇?<br />\n前面冇玩開   但鐘意最初個模式多D"},{"pid":"f6436c8022c298f404ab465033668b092745a062","tid":896672,"uid":180124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T17:41:29.000Z","msg":"睇達哥玩奧德賽都可以勁悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 見到要升呢既已經唔7好玩啦"},{"pid":"3d9629fe7997fa824a30f6d1dea3729d3c8dfaf5","tid":896672,"uid":26491,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T17:46:28.000Z","msg":"呢類單機GAME有兩個重要元素<br />\n1.故事<br />\n2.遊戲性<br />\n<br />\n如果你認為兩個都缺一不可<br />\n咁除左123之外就全部都係垃圾<br />\n如果你只著重遊戲性,咁好似係越新越好既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但就一定唔係呢集<br />\n呢集,劇情根本就係冇,遊戲性,任務重覆到不得了,玩到一半已經唔想玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n為左睇佢劇情玩埋落去,你老母臭閪原來劇情都冇既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"207314de198a5e5882fa3df657a676046ab9044b","tid":896672,"uid":137211,"like":0,"dislike":0,